{"tid":2243887,"cid":5,"subCid":12,"title":"放棄對林鄭的幻想 - 高慧然","createTime":"2020-10-15T05:34:03.000Z","updateTime":"2020-10-15T06:06:29.000Z","uid":25558,"like":2,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":2,"replies":[{"pid":"2d984ccb84424bd084e44c8f9d0a87409cfe7f16","tid":2243887,"uid":25558,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-15T05:34:03.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/columnist/20201015/CX46LCH6TFDUPKQDBMV4ZY54AU/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fcolumnist%2F20201015%2FCX46LCH6TFDUPKQDBMV4ZY54AU%2F&d=LQfwTnO421PZAKP%2FvRgyiX88up93QrsUiEJqOxYGoBw%3D&h=c88434a0\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fcolumnist%2F20201015%2FCX46LCH6TFDUPKQDBMV4ZY54AU%2F&h=daf49904\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.appledaily.com/columnist/20201015/CX46LCH6TFDUPKQDBMV4ZY54AU/</a><br />\n<br />\n節錄<br />\n<br />\n放棄對林鄭的幻想 - 高慧然<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/resizer/2Zo7TeqXp4bQ4xb0f9WMlpYA_Sk=/6720x4480/filters:quality(100)/cloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com/appledaily/CCX6RF25CBAUXASQR3RF2PB77U.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fresizer%2F2Zo7TeqXp4bQ4xb0f9WMlpYA_Sk%3D%2F6720x4480%2Ffilters%3Aquality%28100%29%2Fcloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com%2Fappledaily%2FCCX6RF25CBAUXASQR3RF2PB77U.jpg&h=36607c5d&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n英國記者、人權關注者Benedict Rogers在Hong Kong Free Press（HKFP）撰文，對林鄭的深圳行充滿期待，認為這是一個絕好的時機，林鄭可以當面向中國主席習近平提出呼籲，讓他從輕發落12名被關押至今的香港人。至少讓他們可以請自己想請的律師，讓他們可以定期與律師見面，讓他們可以與家人取得聯繫，確保他們得到適切的治療，健康狀況可以公開。<br />\n<br />\nRogers認為，林鄭已經用無數事實證明了她對中共的忠誠，現在，可以為她的米飯班主香港人做一點點事，盡她作為一個地區長官，對此地民眾的責任。<br />\n<br />\n在Rogers看來，這件事若成功，。。。。。。。。。。<br />\n<br />\n唉，為甚麼到今天還是不明白香港人面對的對手是甚麼樣的人。林鄭怎麼可能為12人發聲呢？她被記者追問得多，已經表現得極不耐煩，選擇了逃避。若有選擇，她情願一輩子裝聾作啞，永遠不必過問這12人的事。<br />\n<br />\n這12人又怎麼可能回到香港，公開暴露在全球媒體鏡頭前呢？他們當日在哪個水域被捉到，是全世界人最有興趣的問題，答案只有他們最清楚。他們會有機會得到公平、公正、公開的審訊嗎？<br />\n<br />\n香港人早已放棄對林鄭的幻想，外國記者也該放棄了。"},{"pid":"a5180e72bd4003a7dbee663e1efa7db8a646c01d","tid":2243887,"uid":228955,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-15T06:06:29.000Z","msg":"可以<span class=\"xx-large\">為</span>她的米飯班主香港人..............  &lt;  On 9"}]}